{"content": "[
  {
    "task_id": "T1",
    "assignee": "David Kim",
    "action": "Conduct performance audit",
    "object": "current REST API endpoints",
    "deadline": "2025-06-20",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 2963,
      "end": 3148,
      "text": "before I can start the API spec, I need to conduct a performance audit of the current API to identify exactly which endpoints are bottlenecks. I'll have that done by June 20th."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T2",
    "assignee": "David Kim",
    "action": "Draft and finalize API specification document",
    "object": "GraphQL and REST API layer redesign",
    "deadline": "2025-06-30",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 455,
      "end": 670,
      "text": "I propose we redesign the core API layer to support GraphQL alongside REST. I'll need about three weeks to draft the API specification document and get it reviewed. I'm targeting June 30th for that."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T3",
    "assignee": "Maria Lopez",
    "action": "Create wireframes and interactive prototypes",
    "object": "analytics dashboard UI",
    "deadline": "2025-07-14",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 821,
      "end": 1042,
      "text": "Once David has the API spec finalized, my team can start on the dashboard UI wireframes. I'll create the wireframes and interactive prototypes for the analytics dashboard. We'll need about two weeks after the API spec is ready, so I'm looking at July 14th"
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T4",
    "assignee": "David Kim",
    "action": "Implement GraphQL API endpoints",
    "object": "new API endpoints based on spec and wireframes",
    "deadline": "2025-08-01",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 1078,
      "end": 1335,
      "text": "once Maria's wireframes are approved, my backend team can begin implementing the new API endpoints. I'll assign two senior engineers to implement the GraphQL API endpoints based on the finalized spec and the wireframe requirements. That implementation phase should take until August 1st."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T5",
    "assignee": "James Patel",
    "action": "Prepare test plan and automated test suite",
    "object": "new API endpoints",
    "deadline": "2025-08-15",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 1402,
      "end": 1639,
      "text": "I'll prepare the test plan and automated test suite for the new API endpoints. We can start writing test scaffolding in parallel with the API implementation, but the full test execution needs the endpoints to be complete. I'm targeting August 15th for full test coverage and sign-off."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T6",
    "assignee": "James Patel",
    "action": "Set up CI/CD pipeline integration",
    "object": "automated regression testing pipeline",
    "deadline": "2025-07-18",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 3654,
      "end": 3882,
      "text": "I'll set up the CI/CD pipeline integration for automated regression testing. That's separate from the API test plan but needs to be done before we can do continuous testing. I'll have the pipeline ready by July 18th."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T7",
    "assignee": "Linda Wu",
    "action": "Develop data migration scripts and perform migration",
    "object": "legacy analytics database to new schema",
    "deadline": "2025-07-25",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 1697,
      "end": 1991,
      "text": "I'll handle the data migration from the legacy analytics database to the new schema. I need the API spec from David to understand the new data models, so I can start after June 30th. The migration script and validation should be done by July 25th."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T8",
    "assignee": "Linda Wu",
    "action": "Validate data migration against live API endpoints",
    "object": "migrated data integrity verification",
    "deadline": "2025-08-08",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 3364,
      "end": 3601,
      "text": "I'll have the migration scripts ready by July 25th but final validation will be done by August 8th, after the core endpoints are up."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T9",
    "assignee": "Maria Lopez",
    "action": "Conduct UI design review and final adjustments",
    "object": "integrated frontend with API endpoints",
    "deadline": "2025-08-22",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 2247,
      "end": 2474,
      "text": "I'll conduct a UI design review and final adjustments once the API endpoints are integrated into the frontend. That should take about a week after James gives QA sign-off and the implementation is done. Let's say August 22nd."
    }
  },
  {
    "task_id": "T10",
    "assignee": "Sarah Chen",
    "action": "Compile stakeholder review package and schedule executive demo",
    "object": "Project Alpha Q3 deliverables presentation",
    "deadline": "2025-08-29",
    "source_span": {
      "start": 2510,
      "end": 2823,
      "text": "I'll compile the stakeholder review package and schedule the executive demo for the end of August. That needs everything else to be wrapped up — the design review, the QA sign-off, and the data migration all need to be complete. I'm targeting August 29th for the stakeholder presentation."
    }
  }
]
